comment: Hill (IND) sets the screen on Irving (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Thompson (CLE) sets the screen on George (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
George (IND) maintains legal guarding position as he defends James' (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Irving (CLE) legally contests Hill's (IND) jump shot attempt. The contact to the non-shooting arm did not affect the shot attempt or follow-thru and is considered incidental.
Love (CLE) faces up with Allen (IND) and clamps his arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.

Thompson (CLE) sets the screen on Hill (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Irving (CLE) knocks Hill's (IND) hand off while backing him down.
